"2018-2024, as compiled from data provided by the 57 vital statistics jurisdictions through the Vital Statistics Cooperative"
"Program. Accessed at http://wonder.cdc.gov/ucd-icd10-expanded.html on Mar 10, 2026 2:36:28 AM"
"---"
Messages:
"1. Totals are not available for these results due to suppression constraints. More Information:"
"http://wonder.cdc.gov/wonder/help/faq.html#Privacy."
